<BaseLayout title="CDN & Netcode · CS Notebook">
  <article class="space-y-6">
    <header>
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary-cyan mb-2">Networks / CDN & Netcode</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">
        <Bilingual><span slot="zh">CDN 与联机优化</span><span slot="en">CDN & Netcode</span></Bilingual>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
        <Bilingual>
          <span slot="zh"><b>CDN</b>（内容分发网络）通过在全球部署<b>边缘节点</b>，将静态资源缓存到离玩家最近的服务器，大幅降低下载延迟。而<b>Netcode</b> 是游戏联机的实时通信优化技术，包含<b>客户端预测</b>、<b>服务器回滚</b>、<b>延迟补偿</b>等策略。两者配合：CDN 负责<b>资源分发</b>（纹理/补丁/视频），Netcode 负责<b>实时同步</b>（位置/状态/输入）。</span>
          <span slot="en"><b>CDN</b> (Content Delivery Network) deploys <b>edge nodes</b> worldwide, caching static assets on servers closest to players, drastically reducing download latency. <b>Netcode</b> is the real-time communication optimization technology for multiplayer, including <b>client-side prediction</b>, <b>server rollback</b>, and <b>lag compensation</b>. They work together: CDN handles <b>asset delivery</b> (textures/patches/video), Netcode handles <b>real-time sync</b> (position/state/input).</span>
        </Bilingual>
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">CDN 工作原理</span><span slot="en">How CDN Works</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
        <Bilingual>
          <span slot="zh">CDN 的核心是<b>边缘缓存</b>和<b>就近接入</b>：<br>
          ① <b class="text-func-amber">DNS 智能解析</b>：玩家请求 <code>cdn.game.com</code> 时，DNS 根据<b>玩家 IP 地理位置</b>返回最近的 CDN 边缘节点 IP（GeoDNS / Anycast）<br>
          ② <b class="text-primary-cyan">边缘缓存命中</b>：若边缘节点已缓存该资源 → 直接返回（<b>缓存命中</b>），延迟通常 &lt; 10ms<br>
          ③ <b class="text-func-red">回源（Miss）</b>：若未缓存 → 边缘节点向<b>源站（Origin）</b>请求，获取后缓存一份再返回给玩家<br>
          ④ <b class="text-func-green">缓存失效</b>：通过 <b>TTL</b> 或 <b>主动刷新</b>（Purge API）管理缓存有效期<br><br>
          游戏场景：版本更新时，补丁文件先上传到源站，CDN 自动分发到全球边缘节点。玩家下载时命中最近的节点，下载速度可达源站的 10-50 倍。</span>
          <span slot="en">CDN's core is <b>edge caching</b> and <b>proximity access</b>:<br>
          ① <b class="text-func-amber">Smart DNS</b>: When a player requests <code>cdn.game.com</code>, DNS returns the nearest CDN edge node IP based on <b>player geo-location</b> (GeoDNS / Anycast)<br>
          ② <b class="text-primary-cyan">Cache Hit</b>: If the edge node has the asset cached → return directly (<b>cache hit</b>), latency typically &lt; 10ms<br>
          ③ <b class="text-func-red">Origin Fetch (Miss)</b>: If not cached → edge node fetches from <b>origin server</b>, caches a copy, then returns to player<br>
          ④ <b class="text-func-green">Cache Invalidation</b>: Manage cache validity via <b>TTL</b> or <b>active purge</b> (Purge API)<br><br>
          Games: On version updates, patch files upload to origin, CDN auto-distributes to global edge nodes. Players download from the nearest node, 10-50× faster than origin.</span>
        </Bilingual>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">CDN vs P2P vs 直连源站</span><span slot="en">CDN vs P2P vs Direct Origin</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="text-ink-muted text-left"><tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><th class="py-2 pr-4"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">特性</span><span slot="en">Feature</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-red"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">直连源站</span><span slot="en">Direct Origin</span></Bilingual></th><th class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green">CDN</th><th class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-amber">P2P</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody class="text-ink">
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">延迟</span><span slot="en">Latency</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-red"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">高（跨洲 100-300ms）</span><span slot="en">High</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">低（&lt;20ms）</span><span slot="en">Low</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-amber"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">中（依赖对等节点）</span><span slot="en">Medium</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[color:var(--glass-border)]"><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-ink-muted"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">源站压力</span><span slot="en">Origin Load</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-red"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">全部承担</span><span slot="en">Full</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">极低（仅回源）</span><span slot="en">Minimal</span></Bilingual></td><td class="py-2 pr-4 text-func-green"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">极低（玩家分担）</span><span slot="en">Minimal</span></Bilingual></td></tr>
